relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented, no acute distress
relevant_findings.heent: No scleral icterus, dry mucous membranes
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, gallops or rubs
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezing, rales or rhonchi
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, tenderness to palpation in right upper quadrant, positive Murphy’s sign, no rebound or guarding, normoactive bowel sounds, no palpable masses
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well-perfused, dorsalis pedis pulses intact
